text: Mesestola guadeloupensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1980. It is known from Guadeloupe.BioLib.cz - Mesestola guadeloupensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Calliini Category:Beetles described in 1980
title: Mesestola guadeloupensis
